summary:
I am aware that I might be kinda late to this but here goes nothing....
We are all aware of the song White horse (which for me...
body:
Sooo umm I have a theory….

I am aware that I might be kinda late to this but here goes nothing….

We are all aware of the song White horse (which for me is one of Taylor’s best songs).

In the song she sings about how she realises that romances \ romantic relationships are nothing like the fantasies she once dreamed of.

Thus the white horse representing an ideal of romance or any ideal of life in general.

Thus in the blank space MV in the parts where she is romancing the guy she represents the ideal parts of the romance by-

Riding on white horses.

In the ready for it MV she shows the good/ ideal Taylor (the real Taylor) sitting on a -

White horse.

For Taylor horses (specifically white)represent ideals.

With the state we are seeing Taylor in rn in her life we can say she is very happy with her life. Her life is ideal.

Now let’s see a date on the reputation calendar-

Dec 13 which is Taylors birthday but is also….

Day of the horse.

So what does this mean?

For me this means that TS 7 will be about Taylor’s childhood ideals for the future and how those dreams/ideals have played out.

Thank you for coming to my Ted talk.
